"快速上手\n1. 可在手表粘贴字体链接直接导入，或在 iPhone 端导入后同步到手表。\n2. 选择样式槽位（正文 / 斜体 / 粗体 / 代码）。\n3. 用上下箭头调整顺序。\n4. 点击“添加字体到当前槽位”补入缺失字体。\n5. 对槽位内字体右滑可“移除”，仅移出当前槽位。\n\n规则说明\n• 每个槽位互相独立。\n• 同一字体可加入多个槽位。\n• 当前槽位无可用字体时自动回退系统字体。" = "Quick start\n1. Paste a font link on Apple Watch to import directly, or import on iPhone and sync to Watch.\n2. Choose a style slot (body / italic / bold / code).\n3. Use the up and down arrows to adjust order.\n4. Tap Add Font to Current Slot to fill in missing fonts.\n5. Swipe a font in a slot to Remove it from that slot only.\n\nRules\n• Each slot is independent.\n• The same font can be added to multiple slots.\n• If the current slot has no available font, the system font is used as fallback.";
"快速上手\n1. 在 iPhone 端完成导入。\n2. 手表端确认工具已同步并按需启用。\n3. 打开“向模型暴露快捷指令工具”总开关。\n\n导入模式\n• 轻度导入：仅名称，配置速度快。\n• 深度导入：解析 iCloud 链接并尝试生成描述；失败会降级为仅链接。\n\n关键项说明\n• 运行模式：\n  - 直连优先：先直接执行。\n  - 桥接优先：先经桥接快捷指令。\n• 自动批准：审批倒计时（1~30 秒）。\n\n提示\n• watchOS 不支持直接读剪贴板，建议在 iPhone 完成导入后同步到手表。\n• 如果工具不可用，先检查总开关和单项启用状态。\n• 如果 urlshim / URL Scheme 在 iPhone 跳转失败，请回到 iPhone 的快捷设定页，复制清单到剪贴板后使用“从剪贴板导入清单”。" = "Quick start\n1. Complete the import on iPhone.\n2. Confirm on Apple Watch that tools have synced and enable them as needed.\n3. Turn on the master switch that exposes Shortcut tools to the model.\n\nImport modes\n• Light import: names only, fast setup.\n• Deep import: parses iCloud links and tries to generate descriptions; falls back to link-only on failure.\n\nKey items\n• Run mode:\n  - Direct first: execute directly first.\n  - Bridge first: execute through the bridge shortcut first.\n• Auto-approval: approval countdown from 1 to 30 seconds.\n\nTips\n• watchOS cannot read the clipboard directly; import on iPhone and sync to Watch.\n• If a tool is unavailable, check the master switch and the individual enabled state first.\n• If urlshim / URL Scheme fails on iPhone, return to Shortcut settings on iPhone, copy the list to the clipboard, then use Import List from Clipboard.";
"快速上手\n1. 在“服务器管理”确认至少一台服务器已连接。\n2. 打开“向模型暴露 MCP 工具”总开关。\n3. 在“能力概览”检查工具与资源是否已发布。\n4. 用“调试面板”验证调用是否正常。\n\n关键项说明\n• 连接状态：已连接 / 聊天使用 / 重连中 / 失败。\n• 自动批准：审批倒计时（1~30 秒）。\n• 调用工具：手动测试工具执行链路。\n• 读取资源：手动验证资源读取能力。\n\n提示\n• watch 端主要用于查看与快速排查；\n• 复杂配置建议在 iPhone 端完成后同步到手表。" = "Quick start\n1. Confirm at least one server is connected in Server Management.\n2. Turn on the master switch that exposes MCP tools to the model.\n3. Check Capability Overview to confirm tools and resources are published.\n4. Use the Debug Panel to verify calls.\n\nKey items\n• Connection status: Connected / Used in chat / Reconnecting / Failed.\n• Auto-approval: approval countdown from 1 to 30 seconds.\n• Call tool: manually test the tool execution path.\n• Read resource: manually verify resource reading.\n\nTips\n• The Watch side is mainly for viewing and quick diagnosis.\n• Do complex configuration on iPhone and sync afterward.";
"怎么用\n1. 添加技能（粘贴 SKILL.md 或 GitHub 导入）。\n2. 确认技能已启用。\n3. 打开\"向模型暴露 Agent Skills\"总开关。\n4. 在聊天中让模型调用对应技能。\n\nSKILL.md 格式\n• frontmatter 必须包含 name 与 description。\n• 正文可写使用说明、参数等 Markdown 内容。\n\n常见问题\n• 模型不调用：检查总开关与技能启用状态。\n• 导入失败：确认仓库地址可访问。\n• 无法本地选文件：可使用链接导入 SKILL.md。\n• 需要更新内容：在技能详情里编辑 SKILL.md。" = "How to use\n1. Add a skill by pasting SKILL.md or importing from GitHub.\n2. Confirm the skill is enabled.\n3. Turn on the master switch that exposes Agent Skills to the model.\n4. Ask the model in chat to call the relevant skill.\n\nSKILL.md format\n• The frontmatter must include name and description.\n• The body may contain usage instructions, parameters, and other Markdown content.\n\nCommon issues\n• Model does not call a skill: check the master switch and skill enabled state.\n• Import failed: confirm the repository URL is accessible.\n• Cannot choose a local file: import SKILL.md by link.\n• Need updates: edit SKILL.md in the skill detail page.";
